Pound Erases Drop Against Euro As Juncker Says IMF May Not Pay Greek Aid

-- B y   E m m a   C h a r l t o n
-- 
2011-05-26T14:15:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-26/pound-erases-drop-against-euro-as-juncker-says-imf-may-not-pay-greek-aid.html
The pound erased a decline  against
the euro after Luxembourg Prime Minister Jean-Claude Juncker
said the International Monetary Fund may not release its portion
of aid for  Greece  next month.  The pound traded 0.1 percent stronger at 86.46 pence per
euro as of 3:13 p.m. in  London . It weakened as much as 0.6
percent to 87.11 pence earlier today. The U.K. currency gained
0.4 percent to $1.6343.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Emma Charlton in London at 
